Package edu.sru.thangiah.zeus.costfunctions Description

Classes that calculate the statistics for each core class level. A cost function class is implemented for each level of the Zeus structure. This class allows for the abstraction of cost function calculation from the core Zeus code. Implementation of these classes may differ from problem to problem.
